headline: Deloitte recognized as a Leader and a Star Performer in Everest Group's Financial Crime and Compliance Operations Services PEAK Matrix® Assessment 2025
summary: Deloitte has been recognized as a Star Performer and Leader in Everest Group's Financial Crime and Compliance (FCC) Operations Services PEAK Matrix® Assessment 2025. Among the 36 service providers, Deloitte was one of 13 that demonstrated strong capabilities across various financial crime and compliance operations, a vast global reach, and a model balanced between cost and flexibility; resulting in being positioned highest on the Market Impact axis.

headline: 2 Reasons to Like EG and 1 to Stay Skeptical
summary: Everest Group has been treading water for the past six months, holding steady at $343.50. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 8.6% gain during that period.
